  [ 69] pushsymb 22 ............................. <#none>
  [ 71] nteq .................................... <pMyWeapon <> #none>
  [ 72] jmpifz [ 85] ............................ if pMyWeapon <> #none then
  [ 75] getprop 686 ............................. <pMyWeapon>
